name: UNCENSORED
description: Power to the people. UNCX stands for UNCENSORED. A decentralized token built to support creators, independent voices and free speech uncensored. No gatekeepers. Just truth. A token built on truth, transparency and uncensored content. In a world where mainstream narratives dominate, UNCX fuels the creators and communities that dare to question, educate, and speak up. Real news. Real value. Real change.
